OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F312A1781711308
OL,3,CStarmer warns Burnham against
OL,4,Cleadership challenge if he wins by-
OL,5,Celection
OL,7,FThe prime minister has warned Andy
OL,8,FBurnham against launching an immediate
OL,9,Fleadership challenge, instead asking
OL,10,Fhim and the Labour party to focus on
OL,11,Fthe election of a new Greater
OL,12,FManchester Mayor.
OL,14,FIf Burnham wins the Makerfield by-
OL,15,Felection he would have to resign as
OL,16,FManchester mayor causing a by-election
OL,17,Flikely to be at the start of August.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G1/8
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
