CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F312A1781711308
OL,3,CStarmer warns Burnham against
OL,4,Cleadership challenge if he wins by-
OL,5,Celection
OL,7,FSpeaking to journalists at the G7
OL,8,Fsummit, Sir Keir Starmer said that if
OL,9,FBurnham wins the Makerfield by-
OL,10,Felection, his focus should instead be
OL,11,Fon helping the party win the
OL,12,FManchester Mayoralty again, calling it
OL,13,F"one of the biggest by-elections that
OL,14,Fwe've ever fought".
OL,16,FStarmer said: "it's really important
OL,17,Fto my mind that the whole of the
OL,18,FLabour Party and Labour movement
OL,19,Ffocuses on that, which is the next
OL,20,Fmost immediate task."
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G2/8
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,313,300,200,140,000,100
PN,31203
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F312A1781711308
OL,3,CStarmer warns Burnham against
OL,4,Cleadership challenge if he wins by-
OL,5,Celection
OL,7,FIf he returns to Westminster as an MP,
OL,8,FBurnham is widely thought to challenge
OL,9,FStarmer for leadership.
OL,11,FThe PM told reporters that "first and
OL,12,Fforemost, I want Andy Burnham to win"
OL,13,Fbut made it clear he did not want that
OL,14,Fvictory to spark a leadership
OL,15,Fchallenge.
OL,17,FHe said: "I don't think there should
OL,18,Fbe a challenge.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G3/8
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,313,300,200,140,000,100
PN,31204
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F312A1781711308
OL,3,CStarmer warns Burnham against
OL,4,Cleadership challenge if he wins by-
OL,5,Celection
OL,7,F"I think history, particularly the
OL,8,Flast government, shows that that isn't
OL,9,Fa successful way for a government to
OL,10,Fbehave."
OL,12,FDespite warning against any leadership
OL,13,Fbattles, Starmer went on to say that
OL,14,Fhe will not walk away from a
OL,15,Fleadership contest if one is called.
OL,17,FHe said: "if there is a challenge,
OL,18,Fthen I intend to fight".
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G4/8
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
