CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F312A1781711308
OL,3,CStarmer warns Burnham against
OL,4,Cleadership challenge if he wins by-
OL,5,Celection
OL,7,FUnder Labour party rules, any
OL,8,Fchallenger must gather public support
OL,9,Ffrom at least 81 MPs but the current
OL,10,Fleader does not need this and can
OL,11,Fstand regardless.
OL,13,FWes Streeting has repeatedly said he
OL,14,Fhas the required backing from MPs and
OL,15,Fhas indicated he would trigger a
OL,16,Fleadership context as early as next
OL,17,Fweek.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G5/8
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
