OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F312A1781711308
OL,3,CStarmer warns Burnham against
OL,4,Cleadership challenge if he wins by-
OL,5,Celection
OL,7,FSubscribe free to our weekly
OL,8,Fnewsletter for exclusive and original
OL,9,Fcoverage from ITV News. Direct to your
OL,10,Finbox every Friday morning.
OL,12,FThe PM also told Sky News that if
OL,13,FLabour wins Makerfield, he would offer
OL,14,FBurnham a cabinet job and said "I want
OL,15,Fhim to have a big role in government".
OL,17,FThis comes on the final day of the G7
OL,18,Fsummit where Starmer has been meeting
OL,19,Fwith world leaders to discuss Ukraine
OL,20,Fand Iran.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G6/8
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
