CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F312A1781711308
OL,3,CStarmer warns Burnham against
OL,4,Cleadership challenge if he wins by-
OL,5,Celection
OL,7,FThe pressure has been mounting on the
OL,8,Fprime minister in terms of defence
OL,9,Fspending after the shock resignation
OL,10,Fof his Defence Secretary, John Healey
OL,11,Fon Thursday.
OL,13,FStarmer told ITV News' Political
OL,14,FEditor Robert Peston that he
OL,15,F"disagrees" with Healey that the
OL,16,Fcurrent military spending plans are
OL,17,Fnot enough.
OL,19,FHe also said that Trump's Iran deal
OL,20,Fwas a "good thing".
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G7/8
